{
  "stem": "1216.2",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 14.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "The adults had to work, whatever work was assigned to them.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "For the children, there was literally nothing.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "We didn't work.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] There was nothing to do.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "There was no school.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 39,
      "text": "There were no books.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 40,
      "text": "There were no toys.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 41,
      "text": "There was nothing except what we had brought, like my doll.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So mostly we just hung around and got into trouble in one way or another.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] The work for the adults was not necessarily according to their profession.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "My father, like my grandfather, was a pharmacist, yet in Westerbork, he had to work in what was then called the metal industry.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Had great big pipes, like sewer pipes, that had to be flattened-- I do not know what for-- with a sledgehammer.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And that's what he did, all day long.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And I don't know how well he did at it.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I do know that we all wore the Dutch wooden shoes.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They had been given us when we first came, in exchange for our own shoes.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And actually, they're quite comfortable once you get used to them.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But they are made out of one piece of wood.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And as a result, the piece that's above your foot doesn't give when you walk.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "The whole shoe comes up.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So in the beginning, you're likely to get sores or blisters or whatever.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And until the end of her life, my mother had bony outgrowth on top of her feet because of the wooden shoes.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "My father invariably got sores on his feet and open-- and open spots.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I got used to them.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I liked them.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I don't think I can still walk in them.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But I have a pair.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We wore our own clothes, in as far as we didn't grow out of them.",
      "word_count": 15
    }
  ],
